LLMs and MCP in Distributed System.

8
00:00:22,675 --> 00:00:26,435
If you have ever been on call for
a microservice based systems, you

9
00:00:26,435 --> 00:00:30,335
already know what that insurance can be
painful, noisy, and slow to diagnose.

10
00:00:30,834 --> 00:00:33,474
In this talk, I'm going
to cover five main things.

11
00:00:34,315 --> 00:00:37,765
While diagnosing incidents in
microservice environments is so hard

12
00:00:38,265 --> 00:00:42,315
how we can use the large language
models or LLMs together with MCP to

13
00:00:42,315 --> 00:00:46,575
assist engineers during incidents,
what kind of context and documentation

14
00:00:46,575 --> 00:00:47,775
we need to make this actually work?

15
00:00:48,275 --> 00:00:51,425
Some lessons learned from
